<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":33974,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvrp.s5Pg.htm?Find=13%2E875%25&amp;Line=293#Line293" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-05-20-34-35-687.jpg?fit=1024%2C469&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-33974"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":35101,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://interactiveswingtrades.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-10-21-09-45-521-1024x459.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-35101"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":33962,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvr4.s1Jqt.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-05-15-53-45-746.jpg?fit=1024%2C463&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-33962"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Most of the IPO proceeds went towards paying off his personal debts related to the Wellness Center.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":34109,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvr4.s1wHe.htm?Find=%222014%20Notes%22&amp;Line=256#Line256" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-07-01-53-06-643.jpg?fit=1024%2C326&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-34109"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":34625,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/$/SEC/IDEA.asp?R=14D5a.x34qp.3m" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-09-04-15-29-818.jpg?fit=1024%2C517&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-34625"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":34112,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvr4.s1uVv.htm?Find=%222014%20Notes%22&amp;Line=10151#Line10151" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-07-02-03-37-435.jpg?fit=1024%2C304&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-34112"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":33987,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvr4.s1Jqt.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-05-23-21-18-939.jpg?fit=1024%2C438&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-33987"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Just to give you an idea of how up to his knees he was on that hotel, he only had to give the company an extra 415 000 shares for his 85% ownership interest.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":34620,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.secinfo.com/dsvr4.s1R1y.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/stocktrades.exchange/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bandicam-2020-02-09-03-43-04-325.jpg?fit=1024%2C159&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-34620"/></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"red-yellow-background-link"} -->
<p class="red-yellow-background-link">At a cost <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="$450 000 000 (opens in a new tab)" href="https://archive.is/n80YG#selection-1099.0-1106.0" target="_blank">$450 000 000</a>, this was a massive hotel.  It included 267-rooms spanning <a rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label="700 000 square feet (opens in a new tab)" href="https://archive.is/LbV0C" target="_blank">700 000 square feet</a>, with a 40,000-square-foot-spa and 28 treatment rooms, all covering 20 acres of land.  <br><br>That's 26 football fields. <br><br>It was his prized possession, and old-school as he was, Mr. Murdock probably wasn't too keen on the idea of somebody else owning a project that he had worked so hard to build when it was right on his land.  </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

<!-- wp:separator -->
<hr class="wp-block-separator"/>
<!-- /wp:separator -->

