<p style="font-size:42px" class="cursive-background-image"><br><br><br><br><br><em>During <em>Dole</em></em>'s <em>first two years as a public company, the company only netted $4.2 million under <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Generally Accepted Accounting Principles...  </span></em><br><br><br><br></p>
